<para style="q1">

<verse number="16" style="v" />Answer me, Yahweh, for your covenant faithfulness is good;</para>

<para style="q1">because your mercies for me are many, turn to me.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="17" style="v" />Do not hide your face from your servant,</para>

<para style="q1">for I am in distress; answer me quickly.</para>
